snippet.title: Hailee Steinfeld's “The Way You Make Me Feel” | Lip Sync Battle Live: A Michael Jackson Celebration
snippet.description:
Hailee Steinfeld sets the stage on fire on with “The Way You Make Me Feel” on “Lip Sync Battle Live: A Michael Jackson Celebration.” Get ready for new performances and stars on Paramount Network! Thursdays at 10/9c.

#ParamountNetwork #LSB #LipSyncBattle #LSBLive #MichaelJackson #HaileeSteinfeld

Subscribe to Lip Sync Battle: http://bit.ly/17wiz6n

Lip Sync Battle is back for another season of epic performances from the hottest stars on the planet! Each week, A-list celebrities go toe to toe, syncing contemporary hits and classic tracks, all for the ultimate bragging rights: the title of Lip Sync Battle Champion. Hosted by LL Cool J and Chrissy Teigen.
